(.claude/skills/secrets/SKILL.md Markdown (Harness Claude) [(name secrets) (description [|How to handle secret values when an authorized task needs plaintext: keep them transient and out of chat, reports, logs, commits, traces, the Nix store, and checked-in files; prefer gopass, sops-nix, and blind pipe-to-sink. Read when a task touches tokens or other secrets.|])] [modules/secrets/full.md])
